replies.body:
Veigar is like my guilty pleasure. But he just gets countered so easily;

Maw/null shields, other magic shields, Untargetable effects, spell shields, normal shields, tenacity, blinks, flash, barrier, cleanse, qss/mercurial, % damage reduction (ever try one shotting a garen as veigar?), cc immunity (olalf), fiora parry, mikaels crucible, tahm's noms, unstoppable abilites. 

BUT THEN, if you cc him, he's screwed.
